💭 Emojicode solution for solving if a given input number is a palindrome
💭 The solution does not use string conversion
💭 https://leetcode.com/problems/palindrome-number/description/

🏁 🍇
	💭Change the value of X to see if it is a palindrome. 
	💭Ex, 121 is a palindrome, 120 is not.

	💭input
	121 ➡️ x

	💭main
	x ➡️ 🖍🆕 c
	0 ➡️ 🖍🆕 r
	
	🔁 c ▶️ 0 🍇
	  r ✖️ 10 ➕ c 🚮 10 ➡️ 🖍 r
      c ➗ 10 ➡️ 🖍 c
	🍉
     
	↪️ r 🙌 x 🍇
  		😀 🔤Is Palindrome! 😊🔤❗️
	🍉
	🙅 🍇
  		😀 🔤Is not Palindrome 😭🔤❗️
	🍉
🍉